      "props": {
        "text": "97M monthly MCP SDK downloads, 10K active servers, 67% of enterprise AI teams on the protocol — the quieter change is how that reshapes an analyst's day. A user-story lens on PR #44 (MCP Onboarding): Claude Desktop calls `list_graphs` and `search_graph` against MiroShark's bundled stdio server, and the web UI becomes the thing the user stopped opening. The product surface collapses into an eight-verb tool catalog pointed at the Apr-21 bi-temporal graph.",
